posting_body: ['AVAILABLE NOW!', 'Welcome to 872 Warfield (#5) located within a small 5-unit building offering a secure entry a fantastic location in between Grand and Lakeshore Ave.', 'This ground level large studio is situated on the ground level and just underwent a complete remodel!', 'Enjoy cooking in a brand new kitchen complete with quartz counters, custom white shaker cabinets, stainless steel appliances (dishwasher included!), subway tile backsplash, and tile flooring, Newly refinished hardwood floors can be found throughout, along with a brand new bathroom (shower/tub combo surround with subway tile).', 'This unit has large closet too!', "Don't pass up the opportunity to be the first to call this place home!", 'FEATURES INCLUDE:', '- Small 5-unit building w/secure entry', '- Full Renovated Studio', '- 2 Entrances (front & back doors)', '- Full electrical upgrade', '- All new plumbing and plumbing fixtures', '- New LED lighting throughout', '- New paint throughout', '- New blinds throughout', '- Newly refinished hardwood floors', '- All New Kitchen w/custom cabinets, quartz counters, white subway tile backsplash, engineered flooring, and stainless steel appliances (dishwasher, refrigerator, and electric range)', '- New bathroom w/cultured marble tub surrounded w/white subway tile, plus engineers flooring, and new vanity', '- All new interior and exterior doors', '- Tons of storage', '- Individual water heater', '- Communal backyard', '- Laundry in building', 'LEASE TERMS:', 'Rental Amount: $2,000 per month (1 year lease)', 'Security Deposit: $2,500', 'Owner pays: Water and garbage', 'Tenant pays: PG&E', '1 indoor cat OK for additional deposit', 'This is a non-smoking building', 'Street parking', 'CONTACT:', 'Vanessa Klein, DRE #02031653', 'Text:', 'show contact info', '***PLEASE CONTACT VANESSA DIRECTLY***']
